posts.description: A day in the life of the Audi RS2 Avant. Developed collaboratively by @audiofficial and Porsche, it broke records from its 1994 launch, becoming the world’s fastest estate car and the first Audi to smash the 250 km/h barrier. Take a bite out of its turbocharged driving experience. Link in bio to video.

As another @fosgoodwood crosses the finish line, we look back at an unforgettable few days, as well as look forward to continuing to celebrate automotive performance all year round. #PorscheFOS #FOS #GW_Porsche
